Asylum Records is an American record label founded in 1971 by David Geffen and partner Elliot Roberts .
It was taken over by Warner Communications -LRB- now the Warner Music Group -RRB- in 1972 , and later merged with Elektra Records to become Elektra/Asylum Records .
After various incarnations , today it is geared primarily towards hip-hop , along with rock and alternative metal .
It is owned by Warner Music Group , and is currently distributed through Atlantic Records .